            "title": "衍生工具持倉限額提高下周三生效",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">證監會公布，由下月2日(下周三)起，恒生指數、恒生中國企業指數和恒生科技指數的期貨及期權合約的持倉限額，將分別提高50%、108%及43%，至1.5萬、2.5萬及3萬份對沖指定資產價格轉變風險的持倉。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">證監會市場監察部執行董事梁仲賢表示，提高持倉限額將會令市場參與者在交易所市場上進行買賣活動時更加靈活。有關修訂顯示了證監會能夠在紓減系統性風險與推動香港金融市場發展之間取得適當的平衡，藉以鞏固香港作為國際金融中心的地位。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15046351-%e8%a1%8d%e7%94%9f%e5%b7%a5%e5%85%b7%e6%8c%81%e5%80%89%e9%99%90%e9%a1%8d%e6%8f%90%e9%ab%98%e4%b8%8b%e5%91%a8%e4%b8%89%e7%94%9f%e6%95%88",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241113_-CR_Source-web_HKEX_02.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-27 18:00:55",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中燃全年盈利升逾2%  末期息0.35元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國燃氣(00384)公布，截至今年3月31日年度﹐公司擁有人溢利32.52億元，按年升2.14%，每股盈利0.6元，末期息0.35元，與去年相同。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國燃氣官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20231127_FI_source-web_00384.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國燃氣官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20231127_FI_source-web_00384.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國燃氣官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">連同中期息0.15元，全年派息0.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">收入792.58億元，按年跌2.64%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司自由現金流46.61億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司年度內無新增城鎮管道燃氣項目，新接駁逾140萬戶居民用戶，較去年同期下降約15.5%；截至2025年3月331日，累計接駁4845.18萬戶居民用戶，較去年同期增長約3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15046306-%e4%b8%ad%e7%87%83%e5%85%a8%e5%b9%b4%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be2-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af0-35%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20231127_FI_source-web_00384_.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-27 18:00:58",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "金管局：首季特定分類貸款比率升至1.98%　資產質素略轉差",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金管局季報顯示，截至3月底，銀行體系特定分類貸款比率升至1.98%，按季回升0.02個百分點；需要關注貸款比率升至2.25%，上升0.1個百分點，連升3個季度。內地相關貸款的特定分類貸款比率跌0.1個百分點至2.27%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">首季零售銀行稅前經營溢利按年升15.8%，由於外匯及衍生工具業務收入、收費及佣金收入都升，但持有作交易的投資收入減少。淨息差1.51厘，按年收窄2個基點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金管局表示，銀行體系維持穩健，資本及流動性充裕。首季資產質素略為轉差，但維持可控。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15046218-%e9%87%91%e7%ae%a1%e5%b1%80%ef%bc%9a%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%89%b9%e5%ae%9a%e5%88%86%e9%a1%9e%e8%b2%b8%e6%ac%be%e6%af%94%e7%8e%87%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b31-98%e3%80%80%e8%b3%87%e7%94%a2%e8%b3%aa%e7%b4%a0-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250622_CR_source_HKMA__02.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-27 18:01:00",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股午後尋底   金融股成跌市元兇",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股在期指結算日先升後回軟，金融股午後拖低大市，小米(01810)支持力量。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數午後跌破上午低位，低見24194，跌131點或0.54%，或暫時低位，現報    </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數半日報5352點，升7點或0.14%，  </p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數半日報8777，跌26點或0.3%， </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里健康(00241)升5.47%，報4.82元；小米(01810)撐市，貢獻恒指71點，YU7正式登場，股價升4.57%，報59.5元; 紫金礦業(02899)升4.92%，報20.65元 ; ，為暫時表現最好三藍籌</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新東方(09901)跌2.92%，報41.6元 ; 中國人壽(02628)跌2.97%，報18.96元 ; 藥明康德(02359)跌2.65%，報75.35元，為表現最差三藍籌股。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金融股成跌市元兇，建設銀行 (00939)跌1.48%，報8元；工商銀行(01398)跌2.17%，報6.31元；滙控(00005)跌0.58%，報94.85元 ; 中國銀行(03988)跌2.11%，報4.64元 ; 招商銀行(03968)跌2.3%，報55.2元，幾隻股份合共拖低恒指68點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15045519-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%b0%8b%e5%ba%95-%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e5%b8%82%e5%85%83%e5%85%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-6.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-27 15:00:57",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "紫金黃金國際傳未來數周招股",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">外電引述消息人士報道，紫金礦業(02899) 旗下紫金黃金國際計劃在未來數周內申請香港招股上市，集資10億至20億美元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"紫金礦業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">紫金礦業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上月，紫金礦業公布，擬分拆紫金黃金國際至香港聯交所上市，發行股份數量不超過發行後紫金黃金國際總股本的15%。集團認為，今次分拆可掌握產業周期與政策紅利的策略舉措，亦為投資者提供參與黃金資產定價邏輯重塑的稀缺機會。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在分拆前，紫金礦業擬將旗下多座境外黃金礦山資產重組整合至紫金黃金國際旗下，相關重組工作目前尚在推進過程中。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15045379-%e7%b4%ab%e9%87%91%e9%bb%83%e9%87%91%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e5%82%b3%e6%9c%aa%e4%be%86%e6%95%b8%e5%91%a8%e6%8b%9b%e8%82%a1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250115_FI_source-web_02899-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-27 14:25:49",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "筆克遠東半年溢利增近11%   中期息與去年相同",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">筆克遠東(00752)公布，截至2025年4月30日止6個月，股東應佔溢利2.12億元，按年增10.76%，每股基本盈利為17.06仙，派付中期股息每股5.5仙，與去年相同。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"筆克遠東2023年度年報封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/00752-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"筆克遠東2023年度年報封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/00752-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">筆克遠東2023年度年報封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">半年收益34.69億元，較去年同期增加17.9%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">核心經營溢利為2.81億元，較去年同期增加5.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">展覽、項目及品牌激活錄得之收益增加20.2%至30.54億元，溢利增加45.0%至2.834億元 ; 博物館及主題娛樂錄得之收益增加44.3%至2.64億元，溢利增加35.1%至2080萬元 ; 視覺品牌激活收益減少35%至1.04億元，溢利減少98.6%至10萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15045060-%e7%ad%86%e5%85%8b%e9%81%a0%e6%9d%b1%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e6%ba%a2%e5%88%a9%e5%a2%9e%e8%bf%9111-%e4%b8%ad%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e8%88%87%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%9b%b8%e5%90%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/00752.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-27 13:40:56",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市｜港股半日跌15點  平台醫療股飆    小米上揚",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股半日升轉跌，收跌15點，小米顯著上揚，其他電動車股弱勢，平台醫療股升，資源股向好。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數半日跌15點或0.06%，報24309，今早開報24451點，升125點或0.52% ，早段見24471，升146點或0.6%，為半日高位，臨近尾段轉跌，低見24301，跌24點或0.1%，為半日低位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米雷軍官方微博\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250521_FI_source-web_01810-YU7.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米雷軍官方微博\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250521_FI_source-web_01810-YU7.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米雷軍官方微博</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135123_source-web_00241阿里健康-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135123_source-web_00241阿里健康-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里健康官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"六福\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240624_FI_source-bp_00590-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"六福\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240624_FI_source-bp_00590-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">六福</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米雷軍官方微博\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250521_FI_source-web_01810-YU7.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米雷軍官方微博</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135123_source-web_00241阿里健康-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里健康官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"六福\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240624_FI_source-bp_00590-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">六福</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數半日報5352點，升7點或0.14%，今早升5363，升18點或0.35%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數半日報8777，跌26點或0.3%，今早開升36點或0.41%，報8840。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日跌3點或0.012%，高水33點 ; 科指期貨半日升11點或0.21%，報5352點，低水1點; 國指期貨升8783，跌25點或0.28%，高水6點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交1624.29億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小米(01810)發布YU 7及AI眼鏡，半日升4.39%，報59.4元，開市價為半日高，升8%，報61.45元，成交居首，其他車股受壓，比亞迪(0121)報123.5元  元，跌1.75% ; 理想汽車(02015)報111元，跌1.42% ; 小鵬汽車(09868)跌2.9%，報72元 ; 蔚來(09866)跌2.58%，報26.45元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">寧德時代(03750)升1.36%，報329元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米雷軍官方微博\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250521_FI_source-web_01810-YU7.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米雷軍官方微博\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250521_FI_source-web_01810-YU7.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米雷軍官方微博</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地網上醫療平台股受捧，阿里健康(00241)勁升6.78%，造4.88元，為升幅最大藍籌；京東健康(06618)升1.77%，報43.15元；平安好醫生(01833)急升8.99%，造8.61元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">高盛料銅價8月將升至今年高位，隔晚美國銅礦股已炒高，港銅礦股熱炒。江銅(00358)炒高5.04%，造14.98元；紫金礦業(02899)彈升4.68%，報20.6元；五礦資源(01208)急升3.83%，造3.8元；洛陽鉬業(03993)抽升6.26%，造7.98元; 中廣核礦業(01164)曾升逾10.27%，最高價見2.47元，半日收升9.38%，報2.45元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135123_source-web_00241阿里健康-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135123_source-web_00241阿里健康-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里健康官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥業股跌，藥明康德(02359)挫2.65%，報75.35元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 石藥(01109)跌1.54%，報7.7元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">香港中旅(00308)大幅波動，半日收挫18.09%，報1.63元，成交8.34億股，裻15.62億元，最高見2.62元，飆31.66%，半日波幅達49.75%，昨天中國旅遊集團公眾號消息，指中旅酒店戰略投資雅閣酒店集團，中旅在昨日收市後發公告指，持續對公司的業務佈局及合進行不定期的研究和戰略檢視，公司尚未就任何建議作出決定，且概無保證戰略檢視將導致任何將予公告或完成之交易。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">冠城鐘表錶珠寶(00256)近10 時忽然大幅飆升，於9:49AM及9:54AM均觸發市場調節機制，半日最高曾見0.91元，飛升119.28%，收升90.36%，報0.79元。成交達31.93億股渉22.9億元，入20大成交額。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">六福(00590)盈利倒退及減派息，股價不跌反升，半日升5.92%，報20.4元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">浙江世寶(01057)開升揚14.89%，報5.94元，半日升2.52%，報5.3元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">獅騰(02562)配股，半日跌1.72%，報19.4元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"六福\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240624_FI_source-bp_00590-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"六福\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240624_FI_source-bp_00590-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">六福</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
